          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Google Search Console provides real performance data from Google at no cost. Rank Math offers the most feature-rich free WordPress SEO plugin including on-page analysis and schema markup. Screaming Frog crawls up to 500 URLs for free. These three tools together cover on-page monitoring, CMS optimization, and technical crawling at zero cost.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What's the difference between on-page SEO and off-page SEO tools?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">On-page SEO tools optimize elements you control on your own pages: title tags, meta descriptions, headers, content, internal links, images, and schema markup. Off-page SEO tools handle external factors: backlink building, domain authority, brand mentions, and social signals. Both matter. On-page is where you start because it's fully within your control.</div>
