          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What are the most important on-page SEO factors?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Title tag (strongest single on-page signal), header hierarchy (H1-H3), keyword in the first 100 words, internal linking (3-5 links per 1,000 words), meta description (affects CTR), image alt text, page speed (2 extra seconds = 103% higher bounce rate), and mobile optimization. Schema markup is increasingly important for AI search visibility in ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini.</div>
